The whole afternoon I couldn‚Äôt stop thinking about how sad my son was when I arrived at the school. A few hours later, when I went upstairs for some quiet time, it hit me that my son may be depressed‚Ä¶just like me.

What I love about this image is the raw emotion that shows just how hard parenting can be sometimes.
